abstract: Palestinian resident of East Jerusalem plows his car into group of pedestrians at light-rail station in northern part of city, killing 3-month-old Israeli baby and injuring eight other people; police say they are treating crash as terrorist attack; driver was shot as he tried to flee scene and later died of his wounds.

headline.print_headline: Driver Plows Into Group in Jerusalem, Killing Baby
headline.main: Driver Plows Into Group at Jerusalem Train Station, Killing Baby, Police Say

snippet: The driver was shot by police officers as he tried to flee, according to the Israeli police, in what was being treated as a terrorist attack....
lead_paragraph: The driver was shot by police officers as he tried to flee, according to the Israeli police, in what was being treated as a terrorist attack.
